        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Adobe 预告 Project Stardust　更强大 AI 编辑工具轻松发挥创意</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/adobe-teases-next-gen-ai-tools-image-editing/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=adobe-teases-next-gen-ai-tools-image-editing</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/adobe-teases-next-gen-ai-tools-image-editing/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:34:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Adobe]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198001</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Adobe 出尽全力开发 AI 功能，除了最近终于正式推出的 Firefly 之外，他们未来还将推出全新的 Project Stardust，功能更加强大。<br /><span id="more-1198001"></span></p><p>Project Stardust 同样加入了生成式 AI 技术，Adobe 以「内容感知编辑引擎」来形容，也就是可以基于现有的图像，分析之后配合用家的指令进行各种编辑，例如自动去除背景物件，修改物件细节或者加入新物件等等。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51700"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DtKeu9tSZYA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>这个功能可望令不少编辑工序变得更加自动化，让用家可以更集中发挥创意，而结合 Firefly，可见 Adobe 未来将会继续以增加 AI 功能为主要发展方向。Project Stardust 将会在后日的 Adobe Max 大会上正式公布，届时将会有更多的详情。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.techspot.com/news/100390-adobe-teases-next-gen-ai-tools-image-editing.html">Techspot</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
