        <item>
            <title>多款廉价 Android 机顶盒被发现后门　内藏恶意软件与中国伺服器暗中通讯</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/android-top-box-malware/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=android-top-box-malware</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/android-top-box-malware/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:01:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[机顶盒]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197986</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>市面上有不少廉价的 Android 电视机顶盒，虽然基本功能上并无问题，但背后可能藏有危险的恶意软件。最近有安全研究团队发现，有多款 Android 机顶盒预载后门，连结成庞大的诈骗网络。<br /><span id="more-1197986"></span></p><p>根据安全研究团队 Human Security 最近的一个报告表示，他们发现了代号为「Badbox」的诈骗网络，规模极为庞大，至少有几百万个装置受到影响，这些装置大多是中国制造的廉价电视机顶盒和平板电脑，在韧体中就感染了 Badbox 恶意软件，消费者购买了这些装置并安装在家中或办公室之后，恶意软件就会自动连接到中国的伺服器，成为黑客可以遥控的僵尸装置。</p><p>报导指，黑客集团可以透过这个分布全球的网络，从被感染的装置入侵家居或公司网络，触发各种类型的诈骗，包括广告诈骗、住宅代理服务、伪造电子邮件和即时讯息帐户，以及遥距执行程式码等。今次研究中确认了有 8 款装置安装了恶意软件，包括 Android 机顶盒 T95、T95Z、T95MAX、X88、Q9、X12PLUS 和 MXQ Pro 5G，以及 J5-W 平板电脑，不过这些产品经常会以不同贴牌和名称发售。他们根据各种线索找到黑客组织的网站，对方声称已经有超过 2,000 万个有后门的装置售出，在线的装置长期都有超过 200 万部。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="2560" height="1037" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1197997" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-scaled.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-694x281.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-1280x518.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-768x311.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-08-at-20.58.10-1536x622.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>研究团队表示，由于恶意软件是在韧体的 ROM 部分安装，因此一般用户无法从产品中移除恶意软件，如果要避免自己的网络遭到入侵，就应该选择可信赖品牌的产品，而不是来历不明的廉价产品。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.humansecurity.com/hubfs/HUMAN_Report_BADBOX-and-PEACHPIT.pdf">Human Security</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/android-top-box-malware/life-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Galaxy S24 Ultra 外形设计曝光，疑弃用圆边机身改用午餐肉风格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:42:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197742</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>拥有超强摄影功能及外壳采用环保材料制成的 Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 已于今年 2 月推出，而下一代旗舰机 Galaxy S24 Ultra 预计于明年初登场。近日就有爆料者利用已掌握的消息来源，制作了 Galaxy S24 Ultra 的外形设计渲染图。渲染图展示了 Galaxy S24 Ultra 或将放弃使用圆边机身，转为较四方、较平面的机身。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35-1280x759.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35-768x455.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.35.jpg 1376w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41-694x419.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41-1280x773.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41-768x464.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.41.jpg 1368w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45-694x431.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="431" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45-694x431.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45-1280x794.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45-768x476.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-12.22.45.jpg 1370w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>外媒《smartprix》报道表示，虽然 Galaxy S24 Ultra 继续配备 6.8 吋大荧幕，但边框尺寸方面缩小了许多，是所有智慧型手机上最窄的边框之一。而该装置将配备 WQHD+ 分辨率荧幕，预计采用平面设计。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186.jpg 950w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197751" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-10.01.52-694x392.png" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-10.01.52-694x392.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-10.01.52-1280x722.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-10.01.52-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-06-10.01.52.png 1372w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（图片来源：<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-first-look/">smartprix</a>）</p><p>另外，手机设有四镜头设置，容纳多个感应器，又为 S-Pen 保留了专用皮套，迎合重视手写笔功能的使用者，并且疑似在右侧边缘添加 UWB 天线。</p><p>外媒及爆料者又估计，Galaxy S24 Ultra 的尺寸约为 162.3 x 79 x 8.7 毫米，采用钛金属框架，预计将使设备重量减轻 1 克，总重量为 233 克。而电池尺寸很可能保持在 5000mAh，并辅以 45W 快充支援。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="in" dir="ltr">Galaxy S24:<br />147 × 70.6 × 7.6mm 6.2&quot; 168g 4000mAh<br />FHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 25w</p><p>Galaxy S24+<br />158.5 × 75.9 × 7.7mm 6.7&quot; 195g 4900mAh<br />WQHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 45w</p><p>Galaxy S24 Ultra:<br />162.3 × 79 × 8.6mm 6.8&quot; 233g 5000mAh<br />WQHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 45w</p><p>&mdash; ICE UNIVERSE (@UniverseIce) <a href="https://twitter.com/UniverseIce/status/1707670666290532628?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.gadgets360.com/mobiles/news/galaxy-s24-ultra-design-specifications-revealed-leaked-cad-renders-4436803">gadgets360</a>、<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-first-look/">smartprix</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
